   <text:p text:style-name="P10">The root element is <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">&lt;collett:project&gt;</text:span>.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_2" text:outline-level="2"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc113_3197818772"/><text:soft-page-break/>Meta <text:span text:style-name="T8">Data</text:span><text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc113_3197818772"/></text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">The first child element of the XML Root is <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">&lt;collett:meta&gt;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Reference_20_Link"><text:bookmark-ref text:reference-format="number" text:ref-name="__RefHeading___Toc123_3197818772">3</text:bookmark-ref></text:span>. This element holds data collected about the project that isn’t under the user’s control.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_2" text:outline-level="2"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc115_3197818772"/>Settings<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc115_3197818772"/></text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">The second child element of the XML Root is <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">&lt;collett:settings&gt;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Reference_20_Link"><text:bookmark-ref text:reference-format="number" text:ref-name="__RefHeading___Toc125_3197818772">4</text:bookmark-ref></text:span>. This element holds all user settings for the current project that are project-specific. That is, any customisation to the app that applies to each individual project.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_2" text:outline-level="2"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc117_3197818772"/>Styles<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc117_3197818772"/></text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">The third child element of the XML Root is <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">&lt;collett:styles&gt;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Reference_20_Link"><text:bookmark-ref text:reference-format="number" text:ref-name="__RefHeading___Toc127_3197818772">5</text:bookmark-ref></text:span>. This element holds all styles used throughout the project’s text documents.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="P29" text:outline-level="2">Project Structure</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P34">The fourth child elemet of the XML Root is <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">&lt;collett:structure&gt;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Reference_20_Link"><text:bookmark-ref text:reference-format="number" text:ref-name="__RefHeading___Toc759_4109413432">Error: Reference source not found</text:bookmark-ref></text:span>. This section holds the tree structure of the project. </text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_2" text:outline-level="2"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc119_3197818772"/><text:span text:style-name="T8">Text </text:span>Content<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc119_3197818772"/></text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">The <text:span text:style-name="T26">fifth</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7"> child element of the XML Root is </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text"><text:span text:style-name="T7">&lt;collett:content&gt;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Reference_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T7"><text:bookmark-ref text:reference-format="number" text:ref-name="__RefHeading___Toc129_3197818772">7</text:bookmark-ref></text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">. This element is the root element for all text documents in the project. This element holds a set of </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text"><text:span text:style-name="T7">&lt;collett:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text"><text:span text:style-name="T10">story</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text"><text:span text:style-name="T7">&gt;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7"> and </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text"><text:span text:style-name="T7">&lt;collett:note&gt;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7"> child elements.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="P30" text:outline-level="2"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc121_3197818772"/>Extra<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc121_3197818772"/></text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P13">The <text:span text:style-name="T26">sixth</text:span> child element of the XML Root is <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">&lt;collett:</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text"><text:span text:style-name="T11">extra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">&gt;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Reference_20_Link"><text:bookmark-ref text:reference-format="number" text:ref-name="__RefHeading___Toc131_3197818772">8</text:bookmark-ref></text:span>. This element can contain <text:span text:style-name="T26">various extra data about the project, including </text:span>a log of the user’s edit history.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_1" text:outline-level="1"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc123_3197818772"/>Meta Data Section<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc123_3197818772"/></text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14">ToDo</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_1" text:outline-level="1"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc125_3197818772"/>Settings Section<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc125_3197818772"/></text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14">ToDo</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_1" text:outline-level="1"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc127_3197818772"/>Styles Section<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc127_3197818772"/></text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14">ToDo</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="P28" text:outline-level="1"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1197_4109413432"/><text:soft-page-break/>Structure Section<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1197_4109413432"/></text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P34">The <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">&lt;collett:structure&gt;</text:span> section contains the tree structure of the project. Each tree is contained in a <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">&lt;collett:tree&gt;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Reference_20_Link"><text:bookmark-ref text:reference-format="number" text:ref-name="__RefHeading___Toc1194_4109413432">6.1</text:bookmark-ref></text:span><text:s/>section, populated by <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">&lt;collett:item&gt;</text:span> elements in a parent/child system.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_2" text:outline-level="2"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1194_4109413432"/>Item Tree<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc1194_4109413432"/></text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P34">The <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">&lt;collett:tree&gt;</text:span> element is the root element of each tree of the project.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P36"><text:span text:style-name="T14">Parents:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">&lt;collett:</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text"><text:span text:style-name="T11">structure</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">&gt;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Reference_20_Link"><text:bookmark-ref text:reference-format="number" text:ref-name="__RefHeading___Toc1197_4109413432">6</text:bookmark-ref></text:span>.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P36"><text:span text:style-name="T14">Attributes:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text"><text:span text:style-name="T11">item</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">:</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text"><text:span text:style-name="T11">class</text:span></text:span>.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P36"><text:span text:style-name="T14">Children:</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21">None.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="P29" text:outline-level="2">Items</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P34">The <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">&lt;collett:item&gt;</text:span> element represents an item of the project structure, like a document or a folder.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_1" text:outline-level="1"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc129_3197818772"/>Text Content Section<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc129_3197818772"/></text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P15">The <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">&lt;collett:content&gt;</text:span> section contains all the user-<text:span text:style-name="T13">provided</text:span> text of the project. Each text document is <text:span text:style-name="T26">contained</text:span> a <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">&lt;collett:</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text"><text:span text:style-name="T11">document</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">&gt;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Reference_20_Link"><text:bookmark-ref text:reference-format="number" text:ref-name="__RefHeading___Toc686_4109413432">7.1</text:bookmark-ref></text:span><text:s/><text:span text:style-name="T26">element</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T13">.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="P30" text:outline-level="2"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc686_4109413432"/>Document<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc686_4109413432"/></text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P34">The <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">&lt;collett:</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text"><text:span text:style-name="T9">document</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">&gt;</text:span> section contains all the documents that make up the body of the project.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="P31" text:outline-level="2">Document Meta Data</text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_2" text:outline-level="2"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc142_3197818772"/>Document Text<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc142_3197818772"/></text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P16">The text of the document is contained in blocks. A block is either a text paragraph <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">&lt;text:p&gt;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Reference_20_Link"><text:bookmark-ref text:reference-format="number" text:ref-name="__RefHeading___Toc144_3197818772">7.3.2</text:bookmark-ref></text:span><text:s/>or a header <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">&lt;text:h&gt;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Reference_20_Link"><text:bookmark-ref text:reference-format="number" text:ref-name="__RefHeading___Toc527_2306438834">7.3.1</text:bookmark-ref></text:span>.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="P25" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc527_2306438834"/>Header &lt;text:h&gt;<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc527_2306438834"/></text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc144_3197818772"/>Paragraph &lt;text:p&gt;<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc144_3197818772"/></text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P16">The &lt;text:p&gt; element represents a text paragraph in a text document of the project.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P16"><text:span text:style-name="T14">Parents:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">&lt;collett:story&gt;</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">&lt;collett:note&gt;</text:span>.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P16"><text:span text:style-name="T14">Attributes:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">text:style-name</text:span>.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P16"><text:span text:style-name="T14">Children:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">&lt;text:f&gt;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Reference_20_Link"><text:bookmark-ref text:reference-format="number" text:ref-name="__RefHeading___Toc146_3197818772">7.3.3</text:bookmark-ref></text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">&lt;text:s&gt;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Reference_20_Link"><text:bookmark-ref text:reference-format="number" text:ref-name="__RefHeading___Toc148_3197818772">7.3.4</text:bookmark-ref></text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">&lt;text:tab&gt;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Reference_20_Link"><text:bookmark-ref text:reference-format="number" text:ref-name="__RefHeading___Toc150_3197818772">7.3.5</text:bookmark-ref></text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">&lt;text:line-break&gt;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Reference_20_Link"><text:bookmark-ref text:reference-format="number" text:ref-name="__RefHeading___Toc152_3197818772">7.3.6</text:bookmark-ref></text:span>.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc146_3197818772"/><text:soft-page-break/>Fragment <text:span text:style-name="T25">&lt;text:f&gt;</text:span><text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc146_3197818772"/></text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P17">The <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text"><text:span text:style-name="T13">&lt;text:f&gt;</text:span></text:span> element represents a text fragment. A text fragment is a region of text with a specific character format.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P19">Parents:<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text"><text:span text:style-name="T18">&lt;text:p&gt;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Reference_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T18"><text:bookmark-ref text:reference-format="number" text:ref-name="__RefHeading___Toc144_3197818772">7.3.2</text:bookmark-ref></text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T18">.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">Attributes:<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text"><text:span text:style-name="T18">text:style-name</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T18">.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">Children:<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text"><text:span text:style-name="T18">&lt;text:s&gt;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Reference_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T18"><text:bookmark-ref text:reference-format="number" text:ref-name="__RefHeading___Toc148_3197818772">7.3.4</text:bookmark-ref></text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T18">, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text"><text:span text:style-name="T18">&lt;text:tab&gt;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Reference_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T18"><text:bookmark-ref text:reference-format="number" text:ref-name="__RefHeading___Toc150_3197818772">7.3.5</text:bookmark-ref></text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T18">, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text"><text:span text:style-name="T18">&lt;text:line-break&gt;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Reference_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T18"><text:bookmark-ref text:reference-format="number" text:ref-name="__RefHeading___Toc152_3197818772">7.3.6</text:bookmark-ref></text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T18">.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc148_3197818772"/>Space &lt;text:s&gt;<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc148_3197818772"/></text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P17">The <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text"><text:span text:style-name="T19">&lt;text:s&gt;</text:span></text:span> element represents a standard space (<text:span text:style-name="T23">U+00</text:span>20). A single space does not need to be encoded <text:span text:style-name="T23">unless it is a leading space.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T23">In other cases,</text:span> this element should be used for the second consecutive space an onward. If the sequence of spaces is longer than two, the <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text">text:c</text:span> attribute can be used to provide a count.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:span text:style-name="T15">Parents:</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T20"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text"><text:span text:style-name="T20">&lt;text:h&gt;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T20"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Reference_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T20"><text:bookmark-ref text:reference-format="number" text:ref-name="__RefHeading___Toc527_2306438834">7.3.1</text:bookmark-ref></text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T20">, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text"><text:span text:style-name="T20">&lt;text:p&gt;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T20"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Reference_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T20"><text:bookmark-ref text:reference-format="number" text:ref-name="__RefHeading___Toc144_3197818772">7.3.2</text:bookmark-ref></text:span></text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text"><text:span text:style-name="T17">&lt;text:f&gt;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T17"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Reference_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T17"><text:bookmark-ref text:reference-format="number" text:ref-name="__RefHeading___Toc146_3197818772">7.3.3</text:bookmark-ref></text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T17">.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body">Attributes:<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text"><text:span text:style-name="T18">text:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text"><text:span text:style-name="T12">c</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T18">.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body">Children:<text:span text:style-name="T18"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T20">None.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc150_3197818772"/>Horizontal Tab &lt;text:tab&gt;<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc150_3197818772"/></text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc152_3197818772"/>Line Break &lt;text:line-break&gt;<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc152_3197818772"/></text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P18"><text:span text:style-name="T17">The </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Source_20_Text"><text:span text:style-name="T13">&lt;text:line-break&gt;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T17">element represents a line break.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_1" text:outline-level="1"><text:bookmark-start text:name="__RefHeading___Toc131_3197818772"/><text:span text:style-name="T6">Extra</text:span> Section<text:bookmark-end text:name="__RefHeading___Toc131_3197818772"/></text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P14">ToDo</text:p>
  </office:text>
 </office:body>
</office:document>